abstract: It covers pressure not to speak out politically and an eating disorder kept at bay as she questions her eagerness to please. What’s missing? Her feud with Scooter Braun.

lead_paragraph: The Sundance Film Festival began Thursday night with the premiere of a new documentary titled “Miss Americana,” though you could have just as easily called it “The Awakening of Taylor Swift.”

abstract: A new poll shows Americans are more likely than not to support President Donald Trump’s decision to order a drone strike that killed an Iranian general, even amid widespread skepticism about his foreign policy overall.

lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — A new poll shows Americans are more likely than not to support President Donald Trump’s decision to order a drone strike that killed an Iranian general, even amid widespread skepticism about his foreign policy overall.
headline_main: Poll: Many in US Support Trump Decision to Kill Iran General

abstract: U.S. President Donald Trump’s special envoy for talks between Serbia and Kosovo said Friday that the two Balkan rivals must remove obstacles that have blocked negotiations for more than a year.

abstract: U.S. Vice President Mike Pence met with Pope Francis at the Vatican on Friday, discussing the anti-abortion march in Washington and telling the pontiff, "You made me a hero" back home by granting him a private audience.

abstract: At a meeting in California, top officials in college sports mulled how to change the rules that would allow athletes to profit from their fame. But new standards won’t happen until at least 2021.
snippet: At a meeting in California, top officials in college sports mulled how to change the rules that would allow athletes to profit from their fame. But new standards won’t happen until at least 2021.
lead_paragraph: ANAHEIM, Calif. — The delegates had long been lining the back of a meeting room by the time John J. DeGioia, the president of Georgetown University, harked back to last year’s N.C.A.A. convention. Back then, the matter of whether college athletes should be allowed to profit from their fame was on the periphery for the leaders of college sports.

abstract: The British police accuse an American woman of driving on the wrong side of the road in an accident that killed a teenage motorcyclist. The State Department says she had diplomatic immunity.
snippet: The British police accuse an American woman of driving on the wrong side of the road in an accident that killed a teenage motorcyclist. The State Department says she had diplomatic immunity.
lead_paragraph: LONDON — The United States has formally turned down Britain’s extradition request for an American woman who was involved in a car accident that killed a teenager last year, a decision that the British government called “a denial of justice.”

abstract: Ms. Thunberg, who has been rebuking world leaders for inaction on climate change, said she was not deterred by critics who called her concerns overblown.
snippet: Ms. Thunberg, who has been rebuking world leaders for inaction on climate change, said she was not deterred by critics who called her concerns overblown.
lead_paragraph: DAVOS, Switzerland — Greta Thunberg, the 17-year-old Swedish climate activist, spent this week inside the halls of power at the World Economic Forum, addressing the titans of global business and politics, huddling with a few of them for closed-door sessions and being publicly belittled by officials from the United States government.

abstract: U.S. President Donald Trump said on Thursday he will release details of his long-delayed peace plan for the Middle East before Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu and his election rival Benny Gantz visit the White House next week.
snippet: U.S. President Donald Trump said on Thursday he will release details of his long-delayed peace plan for the Middle East before Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu and his election rival Benny Gantz visit the White House next week.
lead_paragraph: MIAMI/JERUSALEM — U.S. President Donald Trump said on Thursday he will release details of his long-delayed peace plan for the Middle East before Israeli Prime Minister Benjamin Netanyahu and his election rival Benny Gantz visit the White House next week.
headline_main: Trump to Unveil Long-Stalled Middle East Peace Plan Ahead of Israeli Leaders' Visit
headline_print_headline: Trump to Unveil Long-Stalled Middle East Peace Plan Ahead of Israeli Leaders' Visit

abstract: The British government on Friday condemned a decision by the United States not to extradite an American woman involved in a fatal road accident.
snippet: The British government on Friday condemned a decision by the United States not to extradite an American woman involved in a fatal road accident.
lead_paragraph: LONDON — The British government on Friday condemned a decision by the United States not to extradite an American woman involved in a fatal road accident.
headline_main: US Rejects Extradition Request From UK Over Fatal Road Crash
